and he was so amazed by this Buddha that he made there and then a determination to become self-enlightened a fully self-enlightened Buddha just like this man Dipankara now it's not I don't think it's of any use to try and discuss whether in fact Dipankara ever existed or not because remember Eastern mythology is very circular

