so it's not nothing in other words you don't get anything for nothing you have to go through the training and this training is two-fold it's both the purification of the heart and the growth of the heart heart here meaning our whole disposition our whole disposition so as you know as soon as you sit you can see these hindrances you can see these impurities arising

